      "@type": "cac-grooming:InitialContactPhase",
      "rdfs:label": "MV2 Re-Contact Thread",
      "rdfs:comment": "September 2022: defendant re-engaged Minor Victim 2 via interstate electronic means after MV1 production window closed",
